      "text": "<style=Highlight>It is recommended to first watch the [Far Side of the Moon] event before reading this Vassal Journal.</style>\n\n'Perhaps a caged bird should never yearn for the starry sky.'\n\nA Bloodborn maiden shaped beneath the moon's gaze, she was nurtured by darkness and now stands as second heir to the Bathory family. Aloof, she keeps her distance from all, and her gleaming fangs and bitter words piercing any soul that dare approach. Yet, her demeanor may well be a disguise, masking the sorrow and uncertainty plaguing her inside.",
