      "text": "I discovered that the 'Moonfall Games' was merely a 'Vessel Selection Ritual' disguised in beautiful trappings by the Hall of the Elders. These girls advanced over the corpses of their companions, with absolute strength being the only means of survival through round after round of these 'games.' At first, Lamia too hesitated, but when Girl No. 66 disappeared under the crimson moonlight, she clutched the scythe of fate with trembling hands. The Lamia of today is unrecognizable from her former self—she has become more like a predator, her mere presence a silent warning to all.",
